{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">CAN YOU, THE BABY SHAKER, SAVE OUR WORLD FROM THE INEVITABLE DOOM!?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Shake the Baby! is a satirical old school boomer shooter with a very peculiar weapon system. Experience a mix of tactical levels, fast paced arena combat, unique visuals and CHAOS.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Save the Babies</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After a thousand years of slumber you are awakened by your thirst of violence. You do not know what the threat is, nor does it matter, you must kill. You and your weapon: the baby.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182600/extras/BabyShaker.gif?t=1733531921\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Pick Up the Babies</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The imminent destruction of Earth is near. Find a multitude of supercharged, magnificent babies, giving you a wide variety of ways to kill your enemies with <strong><i><u>style</u></i></strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182600/extras/BabiesInLine.gif?t=1733531921\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Merge the Babies</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Why have 2 small babies when you can have 1 bigger baby? Create the ultimate weapon of mass destruction, by combining the babies you pick up. All of their effects transfer for guaranteed mayhem.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182600/extras/MergingBabies.gif?t=1733531921\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Throw the Babies</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Wheeeeeeee...BOOM! Those arms were meant for throwing things. Feel the goosebumps as your baby makes contact with your target.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182600/extras/BabyHitWall.gif?t=1733531921\" /><